trans-unit.source: do-while loops are very similar to while loops, except the truth expression is checked at the end of each iteration instead of in the beginning. The main difference from regular while loops is that the first iteration of a do-while loop is guaranteed to run (the truth expression is only checked at the end of the iteration), whereas it may not necessarily run with a regular while loop (the truth expression is checked at the beginning of each iteration, if it evaluates to FALSE right from the beginning, the loop execution would end immediately).
trans-unit.target: 这样做，而循环是非常相似的，而循环，除了真相表达在每个迭代结束，而不是在开始时检查。与常规while循环的主要区别在于，可以确保do-while循环的第一次迭代运行（仅在迭代结束时才检查真值表达式），而不一定要与常规while循环一起运行（真表达式在每次迭代的开始进行检查，如果从一开始就评估为 FALSE ，则循环执行将立即结束）。

trans-unit.source: CRYPT_BLOWFISH - Blowfish hashing with a salt as follows: "$2a$", "$2x$" or "$2y$", a two digit cost parameter, "$", and 22 characters from the alphabet "./0-9A-Za-z". Using characters outside of this range in the salt will cause crypt() to return a zero-length string. The two digit cost parameter is the base-2 logarithm of the iteration count for the underlying Blowfish-based hashing algorithmeter and must be in range 04-31, values outside this range will cause crypt() to fail. Versions of PHP before 5.3.7 only support "$2a$" as the salt prefix: PHP 5.3.7 introduced the new prefixes to fix a security weakness in the Blowfish implementation. Please refer to » this document for full details of the security fix, but to summarise, developers targeting only PHP 5.3.7 and later should use "$2y$" in preference to "$2a$".
trans-unit.target: CRYPT_BLOWFISH -带有盐的河豚哈希，如下所示：“ $ 2a $”，“ $ 2x $”或“ $ 2y $”，两位数的成本参数“ $”以及字母“ ./0-9A”中的22个字符-Za-z”。在salt中使用超出此范围的字符将导致crypt（）返回长度为零的字符串。两位数的成本参数是基础基于Blowfish的哈希算法的迭代计数的以2为底的对数，并且必须在04-31范围内，该范围之外的值将导致crypt（）失败。 5.3.7之前的PHP版本仅支持“ $ 2a $”作为盐前缀：PHP 5.3.7引入了新的前缀，以修复Blowfish实现中的安全漏洞。请参考 »本文件 有关安全修复程序的完整详细信息，但总而言之，仅针对PHP 5.3.7和更高版本的开发人员应使用“ $ 2y $”优先于“ $ 2a $”。

trans-unit.source: CRYPT_BLOWFISH - Blowfish hashing with a salt as follows: "$2a$", "$2x$" or "$2y$", a two digit cost parameter, "$", and 22 characters from the alphabet "./0-9A-Za-z". Using characters outside of this range in the salt will cause crypt() to return a zero-length string. The two digit cost parameter is the base-2 logarithm of the iteration count for the underlying Blowfish-based hashing algorithmeter and must be in range 04-31, values outside this range will cause crypt() to fail. Versions of PHP before 5.3.7 only support "$2a$" as the salt prefix: PHP 5.3.7 introduced the new prefixes to fix a security weakness in the Blowfish implementation. Please refer to » this document for full details of the security fix, but to summarise, developers targeting only PHP 5.3.7 and later should use "$2y$" in preference to "$2a$".

CRYPT_EXT_DES - Extended DES-based hash. The "salt" is a 9-character string consisting of an underscore followed by 4 bytes of iteration count and 4 bytes of salt. These are encoded as printable characters, 6 bits per character, least significant character first. The values 0 to 63 are encoded as "./0-9A-Za-z". Using invalid characters in the salt will cause crypt() to fail.
trans-unit.target: CRYPT_EXT_DES -基于DES的扩展哈希。“ salt”是一个9个字符的字符串，由一个下划线，4个字节的迭代计数和4个字节的salt组成。这些被编码为可打印字符，每个字符6位，最低有效字符在前。值0到63编码为“ ./0-9A-Za-z”。在salt中使用无效字符将导致crypt（）失败。

trans-unit.source: CRYPT_SHA256 - SHA-256 hash with a sixteen character salt prefixed with $5$. If the salt string starts with 'rounds=<N>$', the numeric value of N is used to indicate how many times the hashing loop should be executed, much like the cost parameter on Blowfish. The default number of rounds is 5000, there is a minimum of 1000 and a maximum of 999,999,999. Any selection of N outside this range will be truncated to the nearest limit.
trans-unit.target: CRYPT_SHA256 -SHA-256哈希，带有以$ 5 $开头的十六个字符的盐。如果盐字符串以“ rounds = <N> $”开头，则N的数值用于指示应执行哈希循环的次数，这与Blowfish上的cost参数非常相似。默认的回合数为5000，最小值为1000，最大值为999,999,999。超出此范围的N的任何选择都将被截断到最接近的限制。

trans-unit.source: CRYPT_SHA512 - SHA-512 hash with a sixteen character salt prefixed with $6$. If the salt string starts with 'rounds=<N>$', the numeric value of N is used to indicate how many times the hashing loop should be executed, much like the cost parameter on Blowfish. The default number of rounds is 5000, there is a minimum of 1000 and a maximum of 999,999,999. Any selection of N outside this range will be truncated to the nearest limit.

CURLINFO_NUM_CONNECTS - Number of connections curl had to create to achieve the previous transfer
trans-unit.target: CURLINFO_NUM_CONNECTS -为实现先前的传输，curl必须创建的连接数

trans-unit.source: CURLINFO_OS_ERRNO - Errno from a connect failure. The number is OS and system specific.
trans-unit.target: CURLINFO_OS_ERRNO -连接失败导致的错误。该数字是操作系统和系统特定的。

trans-unit.source: CURLINFO_PRETRANSFER_TIME - Time in seconds from start until just before file transfer begins
trans-unit.target: CURLINFO_PRETRANSFER_TIME -从开始到文件传输开始之前的时间（以秒为单位）

trans-unit.source: CURLINFO_PRETRANSFER_TIME_T - Time taken from the start until the file transfer is just about to begin, in microseconds
CURLINFO_PRIMARY_IP - IP address of the most recent connection
CURLINFO_PRIMARY_PORT - Destination port of the most recent connection
CURLINFO_PRIVATE - Private data associated with this cURL handle, previously set with the CURLOPT_PRIVATE option of curl_setopt()
trans-unit.target: CURLINFO_PRIVATE -与此cURL句柄关联的私有数据，以前使用 curl_setopt（）的 CURLOPT_PRIVATE 选项设置

trans-unit.source: CURLINFO_PROTOCOL - The protocol used in the last HTTP connection. The returned value will be exactly one of the CURLPROTO_* values
CURLINFO_PROXYAUTH_AVAIL - Bitmask indicating the proxy authentication method(s) available according to the previous response
trans-unit.target: CURLINFO_PROXYAUTH_AVAIL -位掩码，指示根据先前的响应可用的代理身份验证方法

trans-unit.source: CURLINFO_PROXY_SSL_VERIFYRESULT - The result of the certificate verification that was requested (using the CURLOPT_PROXY_SSL_VERIFYPEER option). Only used for HTTPS proxies
CURLINFO_REDIRECT_COUNT - Number of redirects, with the CURLOPT_FOLLOWLOCATION option enabled
CURLINFO_REDIRECT_TIME - Time in seconds of all redirection steps before final transaction was started, with the CURLOPT_FOLLOWLOCATION option enabled
trans-unit.target: CURLINFO_REDIRECT_TIME - CURLOPT_FOLLOWLOCATION 选项后，开始最终事务之前所有重定向步骤的时间（以秒为单位）

trans-unit.source: CURLINFO_REDIRECT_TIME_T - Total time, in microseconds, it took for all redirection steps include name lookup, connect, pretransfer and transfer before final transaction was started

CURLINFO_REDIRECT_URL - With the CURLOPT_FOLLOWLOCATION option disabled: redirect URL found in the last transaction, that should be requested manually next. With the CURLOPT_FOLLOWLOCATION option enabled: this is empty. The redirect URL in this case is available in CURLINFO_EFFECTIVE_URL
trans-unit.target: CURLINFO_REDIRECT_URL -随着 CURLOPT_FOLLOWLOCATION 选项禁用：重定向URL中最后一个事务中，应要求手动下一步。随着 CURLOPT_FOLLOWLOCATION 启用选项：这是空的。在这种情况下，重定向URL在 CURLINFO_EFFECTIVE_URL 中可用

trans-unit.source: CURLINFO_REQUEST_SIZE - Total size of issued requests, currently only for HTTP requests
trans-unit.target: CURLINFO_REQUEST_SIZE -发出的请求的总大小，当前仅用于HTTP请求

trans-unit.source: CURLINFO_SCHEME - The URL scheme used for the most recent connection
CURLINFO_SIZE_DOWNLOAD_T - Total number of bytes that were downloaded. The number is only for the latest transfer and will be reset again for each new transfer
CURLINFO_SIZE_UPLOAD_T - Total number of bytes that were uploaded
CURLINFO_SPEED_DOWNLOAD_T - The average download speed in bytes/second that curl measured for the complete download
CURLINFO_SPEED_UPLOAD_T - The average upload speed in bytes/second that curl measured for the complete upload
CURLINFO_SSL_VERIFYRESULT - Result of SSL certification verification requested by setting CURLOPT_SSL_VERIFYPEER
trans-unit.target: CURLINFO_SSL_VERIFYRESULT -通过设置 CURLOPT_SSL_VERIFYPEER 请求SSL认证验证的结果

trans-unit.source: CURLINFO_STARTTRANSFER_TIME - Time in seconds until the first byte is about to be transferred
trans-unit.target: CURLINFO_STARTTRANSFER_TIME -直到将要传输第一个字节的时间（以秒为单位）

trans-unit.source: CURLINFO_STARTTRANSFER_TIME_T - Time, in microseconds, it took from the start until the first byte is received
CURLINFO_TOTAL_TIME - Total transaction time in seconds for last transfer
trans-unit.target: CURLINFO_TOTAL_TIME -上次转移的总交易时间（以秒为单位）

trans-unit.source: CURLINFO_TOTAL_TIME_T - Total time in microseconds for the previous transfer, including name resolving, TCP connect etc.

CURL_HTTP_VERSION_NONE (default, lets CURL decide which version to use), CURL_HTTP_VERSION_1_0 (forces HTTP/1.0), CURL_HTTP_VERSION_1_1 (forces HTTP/1.1), CURL_HTTP_VERSION_2_0 (attempts HTTP 2), CURL_HTTP_VERSION_2 (alias of CURL_HTTP_VERSION_2_0), CURL_HTTP_VERSION_2TLS (attempts HTTP 2 over TLS (HTTPS) only) or CURL_HTTP_VERSION_2_PRIOR_KNOWLEDGE (issues non-TLS HTTP requests using HTTP/2 without HTTP/1.1 Upgrade).
